HEADWORD: Exoptile
<hw>Ex*op"tile</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.Gr. <?/
without + <?/ feather, plumage.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A name
